name: s_m_Load_Master_Agency_Detail_from_Import
description: Session to load the Master_Agency_Detail from mysql data to stage to SQLserver for EDW reports using SCD type 2

parameters.name: $Src_Agency_Group_Gw_Domain_AgencyEmail$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select
Agency_Code ,
Agency_Name ,
Agency_Address ,
Agency_City ,
Agency_State ,
Agency_Zip ,
Agency_Contact_Phone ,
Agency_Contact_Fax ,
Agency_fieldman ,
Agency_Group_Code ,
Field_Representative_Number,
Field_Representative_State ,
Field_Representative_Name ,
Agency_Email1 ,
Agency_Email2 ,
Agency_Email3 ,
Agency_Email4 ,
Agency_Email5 ,
Agency_Email6 ,
Agency_Email7 ,
Agency_Email8 ,
Agency_Email9 ,
Agency_Email10 ,
Status ,
M_Address1 ,
M_Address2 ,
M_City ,
M_State ,
M_Zip,
appointed_date,
agency_alpha_workflow
from
(
select
distinct
LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_nup)) Agency_Nup ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_num)) Agency_Code ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_name)) Agency_Name ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(
CONCAT(
COALESCE(ta.agency_str_1,''),
COALESCE(CONCAT(' ',ta.agency_str_2),'')
)
)) as Agency_Address ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_city)) Agency_City ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_st)) Agency_State ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip)) is null or len(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip))
end as Agency_Zip ,
case when replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-') is null or len(replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-'))= 0
then null
else replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-')
end as Agency_Contact_Phone ,
case when replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-') is null or len(replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-'))= 0
then null
else replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-')
end as Agency_Contact_Fax ,
LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.groups_number)) Agency_Group_Code ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep))::text
end as Field_Representative_Number ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state)))= 0
then NULL 
else LEFT(LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state)), 6) 
end as Field_Representative_State,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.name)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.name)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.name))
end as Field_Representative_Name ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1))
end as Agency_Email1 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2))
end as Agency_Email2 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3))
end as Agency_Email3 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4))
end as Agency_Email4 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5))
end as Agency_Email5 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6))
end as Agency_Email6 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7))
end as Agency_Email7 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)))= 0
then null else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8))
end as Agency_Email8 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9))
end as Agency_Email9 ,
case when LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)) is null or LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)))= 0
then null
else LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10))
end as Agency_Email10 ,
ltrim(rtrim(ta.agency_fieldman)) as Agency_fieldman ,
case when agl.Id is null
then 'Cancelled'
else 'Active'
end as Status ,
row_number() over (partition by LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_num)) order by ta.last_modified desc) as rn ,
ag.address1 as M_Address1 ,
ag.address2 as M_Address2 ,
ag.city as M_City ,
ag.state as M_State ,
ag.zip M_Zip,
agg.appointed_date,
agg.agency_alpha_workflow
from
bronze.adm_t_agency ta
left join bronze.adm_agency_license agl
on agl.Agency_Id = ta.agency_nup
and agl.adm_agency_license_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join  bronze.adm_address_guidewire ag
on ta.agency_nup = ag.agency_nup
and ag.adm_address_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
and ag.type='M'
left join bronze.adm_t_members tm
on ta.agency_nup = tm.members_agency_id
and tm.adm_t_members_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join bronze.adm_group_guidewire gw
on tm.members_group_id = gw.groups_nup
and gw.adm_group_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join bronze.adm_field_reps dd
on ta.agency_fieldman = dd.id
and dd.adm_field_reps_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join bronze.adm_agency_guidewire agg
on ta.agency_nup = agg.agency_nup
and agg.status = 'A'
and agg.adm_agency_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join (
select agency_nup,
max(case when email_rnk = 1 then email_address else null end) as email_addr1,
max(case when email_rnk = 2 then email_address else null end) as email_addr2,
max(case when email_rnk = 3 then email_address else null end) as email_addr3,
max(case when email_rnk = 4 then email_address else null end) as email_addr4,
max(case when email_rnk = 5 then email_address else null end) as email_addr5,
max(case when email_rnk = 6 then email_address else null end) as email_addr6,
max(case when email_rnk = 7 then email_address else null end) as email_addr7,
max(case when email_rnk = 8 then email_address else null end) as email_addr8,
max(case when email_rnk = 9 then email_address else null end) as email_addr9,
max(case when email_rnk = 10 then email_address else null end) as email_addr10
from(
select agency_nup,
email_address,
rank() over (partition by agency_nup order by id) as email_rnk
from bronze.adm_agency_email
where adm_agency_email_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31')
group by agency_nup
) ae
on ae.agency_nup = ta.agency_nup
where
location_type = 'P'
and ta.adm_t_agency_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
)a
where
a.rn = 1
order by
Agency_nup asc;

parameters.name: $Lkp_Master_Agency_Detail$
parameters.label: DBConnection_TGT
parameters.customQuery:
select  Agency_ID as  Agency_ID
,ltrim(rtrim(Agency_Code)) as Agency_Code
,Agency_HashKey as Agency_HashKey 
FROM dbo.Master_Agency_Detail
where Row_End_Dt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'--

parameters.name: $Lkp_salesterritory_ref$
parameters.label: DBConnection_TGT
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc as PMS_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc
, salesterritoryrefid as salesterritoryrefid
, GW_Sales_Territory_Desc as GW_Sales_Territory_Desc
, GW_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc as GW_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc
, case when ltrim(rtrim(PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc))='Robert Knightly' then 'Bob Knightly' else ltrim(rtrim(PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc )) end as PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc
FROM dbo.SalesTerritory_Ref ----
